title: Dogtown and Z-Boys.2001.DVDRip.XviD-Gordie
description:
Dogtown And Z-Boys Narrated by Sean Penn and directed by skateboarding legend Stacy Peralta, Dogtown And Z-Boys is the award-winning documentary that took the Sundance Film Festival by storm. 

This is the story of a gang of discarded kids who virtually revolutionised skateboarding with an aggressive style, awe-inspiring moves and street smarts, and, in the process, transformed youth culture forever. Featuring historic old-skool skating footage, exclusive interviews and a blistering rock soundtrack, Dogtown And Z-Boys captures the meteoric rise of the Zephyr skateboarding team from Venice's Dogtown, a tough "locals only" beach with a legacy of outlaw surfing.

Rippad och uppladdad av Gordie.
